{"tid":435882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"15/10 天文台明早考慮改掛8號波","createTime":"2017-10-14T16:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T04:21:43.000Z","uid":15696,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"4ca796f8d8c01171abf1ac76720ada462c3b26a0","tid":435882,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:17:07.000Z","msg":"強烈熱帶風暴卡努已增強為一颱風，按照現時預測路徑，卡努會在明日稍後最接近本港，在香港西南約300公里內掠過。天文台考慮明早改發烈8號風信號，市民明早出門前應留意天文台有關卡努的最新消息。<br />\n<br />\n以天文台現時預測路徑，「卡努」明日將會升呢為「颱風」級別進入香港400公里範圍，至明日下午2時，中心風力會增強至時速130公里，於明日傍晚時份最接近本港，距離只有約260公里，屆時本港離岸會吹烈風程度的東北偏東風，風勢達8號風球的風力。"},{"pid":"588a334adad85a1c051ee1209777c14f1040d281","tid":435882,"uid":64277,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"又星期日打8號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e466376a389d7059d746b021b77088bd591651","tid":435882,"uid":34457,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:19:59.000Z","msg":"慳撚返啦"},{"pid":"d8608362e10d88b0abdbd982a056d7012979e250","tid":435882,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"8號8號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2c73bb60702e9edf904a5a1a38e6f783961660","tid":435882,"uid":62599,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:37:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭風"},{"pid":"d3c7ebad26c701fb6cfacd1e51e330934658fd14","tid":435882,"uid":18800,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:39:02.000Z","msg":"星期一先打得唔得"},{"pid":"1128a673e7bbed4b425786323f0617d50d31a159","tid":435882,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8號8號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no